      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据当地媒体报道，印尼将把一年的出口收入转回国内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级部长表示，印尼将要求大宗商品出口商将部分外汇收入留在境内至少一年，以增加外汇储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
